---
/* FAQ Section — Accordion with native details/summary | Neon Architect */
---

<section id="faq" class="bg-surface py-[var(--spacing-section-gap)]">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">

    <!-- Ghosted headline -->
    <h2 class="font-display text-[length:var(--font-size-h1)] font-black uppercase tracking-tighter italic text-on-surface/10 text-center mb-20 reveal">
      Questions Fr&eacute;quentes
    </h2>

    <!-- FAQ list -->
    <div class="space-y-0">

      <!-- Q1 -->
      <details class="group border-b border-outline-variant/15 py-8 reveal delay-1">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer font-display font-black text-xl md:text-2xl uppercase tracking-tighter text-on-surface">
          <span>Je ne connais rien &agrave; Make ou n8n, c'est pour moi ?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon text-primary w-8 h-8 shrink-0 ml-6 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="mt-6 text-on-surface-variant text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl font-light">
          Oui. Le programme part de z&eacute;ro. Tu apprendras la logique des APIs et de l'automatisation &eacute;tape par &eacute;tape. Pas besoin de savoir coder &mdash; on utilise le no-code comme un acc&eacute;l&eacute;rateur.
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- Q2 -->
      <details class="group border-b border-outline-variant/15 py-8 reveal delay-2">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer font-display font-black text-xl md:text-2xl uppercase tracking-tighter text-on-surface">
          <span>Combien de temps par semaine faut-il investir ?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon text-primary w-8 h-8 shrink-0 ml-6 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="mt-6 text-on-surface-variant text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl font-light">
          Pr&eacute;vois 5 &agrave; 8 heures par semaine entre les vid&eacute;os, les lives et la pratique. C'est compatible avec une activit&eacute; en parall&egrave;le, mais il faut &ecirc;tre r&eacute;gulier.
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- Q3 -->
      <details class="group border-b border-outline-variant/15 py-8 reveal delay-3">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer font-display font-black text-xl md:text-2xl uppercase tracking-tighter text-on-surface">
          <span>Est-ce que le bootcamp est finan&ccedil;able ?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon text-primary w-8 h-8 shrink-0 ml-6 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="mt-6 text-on-surface-variant text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl font-light">
          Le financement OPCO est possible selon ton statut. Nous n'utilisons pas le CPF volontairement &mdash; cela nous permet de mettre &agrave; jour le contenu en temps r&eacute;el face aux &eacute;volutions de l'IA.
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- Q4 -->
      <details class="group border-b border-outline-variant/15 py-8 reveal delay-4">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer font-display font-black text-xl md:text-2xl uppercase tracking-tighter text-on-surface">
          <span>Que se passe-t-il apr&egrave;s les 12 semaines ?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon text-primary w-8 h-8 shrink-0 ml-6 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="mt-6 text-on-surface-variant text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl font-light">
          Tu gardes l'acc&egrave;s &agrave; la communaut&eacute;, aux mises &agrave; jour des formations et au r&eacute;seau. L'objectif est que tu sois autonome et op&eacute;rationnel pour signer tes premi&egrave;res missions.
        </div>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
